Pehle, jo <div>, <section>, <h2>, <img> jaise tags hain, woh HTML tags hain. Yeh page ka structure banate hain.

<section>: Aapke page ka ek bada hissa (section) define karta hai.

<div>: Ek "division" ya box hai jiske andar aap doosra content rakhte hain. Yeh content ko group karne ke kaam aata hai.

<h2>: Ek Heading (badi title) hai. Yahan "Our Featured Collections" likha hai.

<img>: Ek image (photo) dikhata hai.

<h5>: Ek choti heading (sub-title) hai. Jaise "Luxury Sofas".

<p>: Ek paragraph (text) hai.

<a>: Ek link (hyperlink) hai, jisse yahan button banaya gaya hai.

